cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS 

This paper discusses the security and privacy concerns in Hadoop, which is a popular big data platform. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also proposes a framework for secure access control, which involves database management (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The implementation of the framework involves software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures (cs.DS).
